      <title>道明银行全球反洗钱官员辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/td-banks-global-anti-money-laundering-officer-steps-down-sources-say-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道明银行周四表示，首席全球反洗钱官 Herbert Mazariegos 将立即辞职，因为该行在因合规失败而被美国监管机构罚款后正在采取补救措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/td-banks-global-anti-money-laundering-officer-steps-down-sources-say-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 22:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通首席执行官戴蒙在创纪录利润后 2024 年加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-ceo-dimons-2024-compensation-rises-about-8-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通周四表示，在交易和融资活动复苏的推动下，该行实现了创纪录的利润，长期任职的首席执行官杰米戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 的 2024 年薪酬将上涨约 8.3%，至 3900 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-ceo-dimons-2024-compensation-rises-about-8-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 21:33:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普命令加密货币工作组起草新法规，探索国家储备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-signs-order-create-cryptocurrency-working-group-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周四下令成立一个加密货币工作组，负责提出新的数字资产监管法规，并探索建立国家加密货币储备，兑现其迅速改革美国加密政策的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-signs-order-create-cryptocurrency-working-group-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 20:23:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通警告称，新兴经济体面临资本流动“突然停止”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-economies-facing-sudden-stop-capital-flows-jpmorgan-warns-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资银行摩根大通周四警告称，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统的“美国优先”政策刺激美国经济并吸走较贫穷国家的资金，新兴市场可能正经历可怕的资本流动“突然停止”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-economies-facing-sudden-stop-capital-flows-jpmorgan-warns-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 18:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚下令冻结与前政权有关的银行账户</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/syria-orders-freeze-bank-accounts-linked-former-regime-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社看到的文件和知情人士透露，叙利亚央行已下令商业银行冻结所有与前总统巴沙尔·阿萨德政权有关的个人和公司有关的账户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/syria-orders-freeze-bank-accounts-linked-former-regime-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:47:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向保守派抱怨美国银行和摩根大通拒绝提供服务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/trump-accuses-bank-america-jpm-not-doing-business-with-conservatives-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周四指责美国银行和摩根大通的首席执行官没有向保守派提供银行服务，这与共和党对该行业的抱怨如出一辙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/trump-accuses-bank-america-jpm-not-doing-business-with-conservatives-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普渡制药与萨克勒达成 74 亿美元全国阿片类药物和解协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/purdue-pharma-sacklers-reach-74-bln-national-opioid-settlement-2025-01-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国多个州的总检察长周四表示，普渡制药及其所有者萨克勒家族已达成一项新的 74 亿美元的和解协议，以解决数千起诉讼，这些诉讼指控止痛药奥施康定在美国引发了大规模阿片类药物成瘾危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/purdue-pharma-sacklers-reach-74-bln-national-opioid-settlement-2025-01-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
